Create empty stack S Set x=0, flag=0, sum=0 Push x onto S while (S is not empty){ if (flag equals 0){ Set x = x+1 Push x onto S} if (x equals 8): Set flag=1 if (flag equals 1){ x = Pop(S) if (x is odd): Pop(S) Set sum = sum + x} } Output sum The value of sum output by a program executing the above pseudocode is _________. (Answer in integer)
